### Logout
GET  http://localhost:4000/common-api/logout



### Create article (AUTHOR)
POST http://localhost:4000/author-api/article
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author":"69afe0a84076aff12d3c4a53",
  "title":"Naruto",
  "category":"Anime",
  "content":"this anime is a Ninja related!"
}



###Read articles of a author
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/698acc809350f1a90ca54e2b



### Update article (AUTHOR)
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author":"698acc809350f1a90ca54e2b",
  "articleId":"698accde9350f1a90ca54e31",
  "title":"test2 article updated",
  "category":"programming",
  "content":"content of test2 article updated"
}
